skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: army ranks review
des: Alexa can help you to learn the many Army Ranks for the U.S. Military. You can review the flash cards and then test your knowledge. At any point you can say "Alexa, review mode" to switch to review or say "Alexa, test mode" to start a test. You can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next card. At any point during the test, you can say "Alexa, what's my score" to get your current test score. This will help you, as a civilian, to learn what each rank is and as a new soldier, to learn the command rank structure.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
